          </div>
          <div class="cost-card reveal-item" data-reveal="fade-up" style="--delay: 400ms;">
            <span class="cost-number">7-8%</span>
            <span class="cost-label">Annual Increase</span>
            <p>Expected healthcare cost growth for US employers in 2025.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cost-card reveal-item" data-reveal="fade-up" style="--delay: 500ms;">
            <span class="cost-number">2.5√ó</span>
            <span class="cost-label">vs Working Age</span>
            <p>Per-capita spending for 65+ compared to working-age adults.</p>
          </div>
