        <span class="badge badge-green reveal-item" data-reveal="fade-up" style="--delay: 0ms;">The Opportunity</span>
        <h2 class="headline reveal-item" data-reveal="fade-up" style="--delay: 100ms;">Biotech Can Bend the Cost Curve</h2>
        <p class="statement reveal-item" data-reveal="fade-up" style="--delay: 200ms;">
          Solutions that extend healthspan, reduce costs, and improve lives
        </p>
        <p class="closing-subtext reveal-item" data-reveal="fade-up" style="--delay: 400ms;">
          If 90% of spend is tied to chronic conditions linked to aging, even single-digit
          percentage reductions cascade into hundreds of billions in savings.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- =========================================================================
         SECTION 7: Global Aging Wave - Hero
         ========================================================================= -->
    <section class="slide slide-aging-hero" id="global-aging">
      <div class="slide-gradient slide-gradient-purple"></div>
      <div class="slide-content slide-content-center">
        <p class="eyebrow reveal-item" data-reveal="fade-up" style="--delay: 0ms;">Why Now</p>
        <h1 class="headline reveal-item" data-reveal="fade-up" style="--delay: 100ms;">The Global Aging Wave</h1>
        <p class="statement reveal-item" data-reveal="fade-up" style="--delay: 200ms;">
          A demographic shift creating a multi-trillion dollar opportunity
        </p>
        <div class="big-stat reveal-item" data-reveal="scale-up" style="--delay: 400ms;">
          <span class="big-stat-number">2B</span>
          <p class="big-stat-label">people over 60 by 2050</p>
          <p class="big-stat-source">United Nations</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- =========================================================================
         SECTION 8: Demographic Statistics
         ========================================================================= -->
    <section class="slide slide-demo-stats" id="demo-stats">
      <div class="slide-gradient"></div>
      <div class="slide-content">
        <span class="badge badge-purple reveal-item" data-reveal="fade-up" style="--delay: 0ms;">Demographics</span>
        <h2 class="section-title-centered reveal-item" data-reveal="fade-up" style="--delay: 100ms;">A Defining Global Trend</h2>
