          </div>
          <div class="path-point reveal-item" data-reveal="fade-up" style="--delay: 500ms;">
            <h4>Mainstream Theme</h4>
            <p>Longevity-focused biotechs raised over $2 billion via IPOs in 2023 alone.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="path-point reveal-item" data-reveal="fade-up" style="--delay: 600ms;">
            <h4>Data-Driven Stories</h4>
